reviewText:
Very informative. A nice history of the castle.

 The narrator states there is always a crime behind every great fortune. Leftist?

As someone who has a yearning to return and visit Skibo castle, this is the next best thing to being there. The tour includes many interior rooms and exterior landscaping. Historical and present day location context / narration and old photographs complete this wonderful DVD. I am encouraged to purchase other America's Castles DVDs.
